> > > > book in the index, you split it up in single pages and index them. =
Now
> > > > it's faster if a page changes or is deleted to update your index in=
stead
> > > > of doing it over and over again for all 1000 pages. So you problem =
starts
> > > > when you're searching on the book. You search for (foo bar), foo is=
