William,

The order of the results are going to be based on how well they match the=20
query (i.e. weighted by relevancy).  So although all of those values=20
contain the term "Palm", I would assume you would get the shorter entries=20
(i.e. 1 & 3) before the longer ones (2) as they have a higher percentage of=
=20
"palmness".  Same goes for the second query (it is a better match for 1,=20
than 2).  If you want the documents to come back in their document order,=20
you would need to sort the results yourself.

-Mike

