Subject: Re: mergeFactor and maxMergeDocs


Obsession with indexing performance is not healthy.  Before changing any =

settings convince yourself that indexing performance is a real problem=20
for your application.  How often do you re-index from scratch?  Are you=20
really having any difficulty keeping up with the rate of change of your=20
collection?  Perhaps your development time would be better spent=20
focussing on other parts of your application.

