Hi,

this works in my program:


        RAMDirectory ramDir =3D new RAMDirectory();
        IndexWriter ram_writer_de =3D new IndexWriter(ramDir,
                            new GermanAnalyzer(), true);
        // my method to fill the index
        fillIndex(ram_writer_de);
        ram_writer_de.optimize();
        IndexWriter fs_writer_de =3D  new IndexWriter(HOME_DIR + "de/",
                            new GermanAnalyzer(), true);
        fs_writer_de.addIndexes(new Directory[]{ramDir});

        fs_writer_de.close();
        ram_writer_de.close();


regards

Hanjo

